the best table at my hotel’s bar, by the fireplace. Even though she’d been living in Asia until recently, Laura has been an attentive follower of our recipes and Shop. Some of her favorite purchases include this \u003ca href=\"https://food52.com/shop/products/13439-studio-joo-porcelain-handmade-ceramic-serving-bowl?utm_content=A\"\u003ehandmade porcelain serving bowl by Studio Joo\u003c/a\u003e and seven—seven!—of the \u003ca href=\"https://food52.com/shop/products/7503-hasegawa-lucano-step-ladder?utm_content=A\"\u003eHasegawa step ladders\u003c/a\u003e, in all different sizes. As a single step ladder owner, I bow to her midheight domestic emergency preparedness!\u003c/p\u003e\n              \n\n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\n      \u003ca href=\"https://www.pinterest.com/pin/create/button\" data-pin-do=\"buttonPin\" data-pin-media=\"\" data-pin-custom=\"true\" data-ga-event=\"inPageInteraction\" data-ga-event-action=\"Pinterest Share\" data-ga-event-label=\"Article Body Image\" data-ga-destination-url=\"none\"\u003e\n        \u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 16.9 20.8\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M16.8 6.3C16.5 3.2 13.6.4 10.1.1 4.8-.5.1 2.7 0 7.9c0 2.4.8 4 2.9 4.8 1.5-1.5-.3-2.4-.5-4C2 4.3 7.1.1 11.7 2.9c3.2 1.9 2.6 9.9-1.2 10.7-.8.1-1.8-.1-2.1-.5-1.9-1.8 1.5-4.8.4-7.3-.9-2.1-3.6-.4-3.9 1.5-.2 1 .3 2 .3 2.9 0 2.1-1.3 5-1.7 7.1-.2.9-.3 2.6-.1 3.4h1.5c1-1.6 1.6-4.1 2.1-6.3.3-.2.5.4.7.6 1.8 1.4 5 .6 6.4-.7 2.1-1.7 3-5.2 2.7-8\" fill=\"currentColor\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\n      \u003c/a\u003e\n\n      \u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" media=\"(min-width: 1400px)\" type=\"image/webp\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/ln1-lFeID6ZHjK5f3EwPpjo9hwQ=/778x778/filters:format(webp)/0de8cd16-2af1-48a5-a3a3-8e1ad6f910e7--image7.jpg, https://images.food52.com/5EFERlyNCmXNewpuL5ytYzUd2Mw=/1556x1556/filters:format(webp)/0de8cd16-2af1-48a5-a3a3-8e1ad6f910e7--image7.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" media=\"(min-width: 1400px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/guAq5_pcw7GAbXlpC_t4AG9uIk8=/778x778/0de8cd16-2af1-48a5-a3a3-8e1ad6f910e7--image7.jpg, https://images.food52.com/WR2EBmyTJG3BBuk5cmNXSXOSrd4=/1556x1556/0de8cd16-2af1-48a5-a3a3-8e1ad6f910e7--image7.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" type=\"image/webp\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/KKUVrEqG0QMnCqT7cU7Db7Ybt70=/660x660/filters:format(webp)/0de8cd16-2af1-48a5-a3a3-8e1ad6f910e7--image7.jpg, https://images.food52.com/kh_iv4HAeKzYcx2gabeRhtc2v48=/1320x1320/filters:format(webp)/0de8cd16-2af1-48a5-a3a3-8e1ad6f910e7--image7.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/mveOaFeMDp98QpYUZGxWpuhgVCA=/660x660/0de8cd16-2af1-48a5-a3a3-8e1ad6f910e7--image7.jpg, https://images.food52.com/cE5eke3JsPFGjjPOKmMjMRgQedc=/1320x1320/0de8cd16-2af1-48a5-a3a3-8e1ad6f910e7--image7.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" type=\"image/webp\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/GsoPhNyEKPlLDJ25TXIeNZeOeoM=/964x964/filters:format(webp)/0de8cd16-2af1-48a5-a3a3-8e1ad6f910e7--image7.jpg, https://images.food52.com/7ztGgX3tXotZkoulyw04-Q7YikE=/1928x1928/filters:format(webp)/0de8cd16-2af1-48a5-a3a3-8e1ad6f910e7--image7.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/aPlYpjq-1Fk9VqOl1qio_Z7ff4c=/964x964/0de8cd16-2af1-48a5-a3a3-8e1ad6f910e7--image7.jpg, https://images.food52.com/mN02mpZxXR692NSEgmV7H1CqJQ0=/1928x1928/0de8cd16-2af1-48a5-a3a3-8e1ad6f910e7--image7.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" media=\"(min-width: 500px)\" type=\"image/webp\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/J9bhPpdzDGF40z7Jf2xGv9sGHJo=/768x768/filters:format(webp)/0de8cd16-2af1-48a5-a3a3-8e1ad6f910e7--image7.jpg, https://images.food52.com/IXY9z-mkaY8835vpNBJ_DbMsX3c=/1536x1536/filters:format(webp)/0de8cd16-2af1-48a5-a3a3-8e1ad6f910e7--image7.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" media=\"(min-width: 500px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/ByWj885_186ZAvuR9zu2ZP2CIwY=/768x768/0de8cd16-2af1-48a5-a3a3-8e1ad6f910e7--image7.jpg, https://images.food52.com/6uHqjx_1JxbitgWK-rPHyI0wJLw=/1536x1536/0de8cd16-2af1-48a5-a3a3-8e1ad6f910e7--image7.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" type=\"image/webp\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/ypMgaCmvnc0jWtt0lJDSDlEqrXc=/375x375/filters:format(webp)/0de8cd16-2af1-48a5-a3a3-8e1ad6f910e7--image7.jpg, https://images.food52.com/nvuG0HLqMEorkPPFM415ANxrcd8=/750x750/filters:format(webp)/0de8cd16-2af1-48a5-a3a3-8e1ad6f910e7--image7.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003cimg srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/yMkxrCJYI9bE6AdSByRagXJNz-E=/375x375/0de8cd16-2af1-48a5-a3a3-8e1ad6f910e7--image7.jpg, https://images.food52.com/pClWilmF3UVOt3mRgglkMrueR-I=/750x750/0de8cd16-2af1-48a5-a3a3-8e1ad6f910e7--image7.jpg 2x\" alt=\"\" width=\"964\" height=\"964\" data-expand=\"750\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/yMkxrCJYI9bE6AdSByRagXJNz-E=/375x375/0de8cd16-2af1-48a5-a3a3-8e1ad6f910e7--image7.jpg, https://images.food52.com/pClWilmF3UVOt3mRgglkMrueR-I=/750x750/0de8cd16-2af1-48a5-a3a3-8e1ad6f910e7--image7.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n      \u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n          \u003cspan\u003ePhoto by Amanda Hesser\u003c/span\u003e\n      \u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n              \u003cp\u003eI also had a beer with Charlie at the Mallard Lounge in the Fairmont Hotel. Charlie has her own catering company, \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/sobremesa.eats/?utm_content=A\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eSobremesa Catering\u003c/a\u003e, in Vancouver and Whistler. She shared a lot of good local details, everything from the ski/snowboarding pants of the moment—very baggy, like \u003ca href=\"https://www.snowverb.com/collections/womens-snowboard-pants-bibs/products/womens-rabbit-snow-prime-cargo-baggy-snowboard-pants?variant=40966660456491\u0026amp;utm_content=A\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ethese\u003c/a\u003e—to the quality of life in Whistler (the tax base is so high that the local sanitation department broadcasts jazz music at the town dump). After we met, she went home and made this \u003ca href=\"https://food52.com/recipes/9554-michael-field-s-fondue/amp?utm_content=A\"\u003efondue recipe\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \n              \u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWe’ve been writing up our home design predictions for the new year, including the \u003ca href=\"https://food52.com/blog/28593-best-paint-colors-2025?utm_content=A\"\u003epaint colors\u003c/a\u003e that designers think will take over in 2025. Pantone says Mocha Mousse is the shade to watch out for—thankfully we have plenty of it \u003ca href=\"https://food52.com/blog/28575-pantone-color-of-the-year-2025-mocha-mousse?utm_content=A\"\u003ein our Shop\u003c/a\u003e, and it also appears in our recipes. We’ll be making more predictions in the coming days, so stay tuned.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eIt’s time, sadly, to start taking down the tree—here’s \u003ca href=\"https://food52.com/blog/28603-how-to-store-christmas-ornaments?utm_content=A\"\u003ehow to store Christmas ornaments safely\u003c/a\u003e. (Spoiler alert: These \u003ca href=\"https://food52.com/shop/products/13530-like-it-rolling-stackable-containers-with-tray?utm_content=A\"\u003eLike-it rolling bins\u003c/a\u003e are key!)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNoah did a 2-part Instagram how-to on \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/reel/DEEItvFxaXS/?igsh=QkFKalhvVy1ZeA%3D%3D\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eporchetta\u003c/a\u003e. It’s pleasing even if you never plan to make porchetta, though I think you should.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003eVery best wishes for serene and distraction-free focus in the days and months ahead!\u003c/p\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003eAmanda\u003c/p\u003e\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n\n            \n    \n\n\n            \n            \n\n\n\n            \n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n\n    \u003cp\u003e\n      Before starting Food52 with Merrill, I was a food writer and editor at the New York Times. I\u0026#39;ve written several books, including \u0026#34;Cooking for Mr. Latte\u0026#34; and \u0026#34;The Essential New York Times Cookbook.\u0026#34; I played myself in \u0026#34;Julie \u0026amp; Julia\u0026#34; -- hope you didn\u0026#39;t blink, or you may have missed the scene! I live in Brooklyn with my husband, Tad, and twins, Walker and Addison.\n    \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \n  \u003cdiv\u003e\n      \u003ch3\u003ePopular on Food52\u003c/h3\u003e\n      \n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
